{"tid":285111,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"小四生一元利誘婆婆摸胸 食環署突然現身拉人『你賣一蚊都係無牌小販』","createTime":"2017-06-15T13:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T13:49:43.000Z","uid":78620,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dcd5e8ded720f4b4352fc17bc5b4c0fb732a9ba","tid":285111,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"小四生一元利誘婆婆摸胸 食環署突然現身拉人『你賣一蚊都係無牌小販』<br />\n<br />\n黎志強指，日前收到朱婆婆求助，央求他撰寫法庭求情信；黎指，朱婆婆年屆75歲，獨居於柴灣興華邨，雖然家貧，惟因不願領取綜援，故向朋友借手推車，以執拾並轉售紙皮賺取生活費，「婆婆話當日佢喺中環碼頭近摩天輪一帶執紙皮，執咗幾個，突然有小學三年級生話要同佢摸胸，咁婆婆無乜所謂，就按對方要求賣一蚊」。<br />\n<br />\n黎引述朱婆婆所言，當日甫賣出紙皮即有食環職員現身，並控告她無牌販賣。據悉，涉案小色魔早於去年讀小學三年級開始，以每次一至五元利誘婆婆，「婆婆無辦法，因為現場人贓並獲，百詞莫辯，雖然都有向食環求情，但對方就話『你賣一蚊都係無牌小販』」<br />\n<br />\n未達刑責年齡<br />\n司警發言人昨日稱，涉案男生年齡只在小童階段，未達至須負上刑責之年齡，但其行為已構成道德問題。警方呼籲家長留意子女的日常行為，切勿讓子女透過互聯網接觸不良及色情資訊，更應灌輸正確的性觀念。"},{"pid":"e6311e22140450e42110e414e1b67514fe66ad8d","tid":285111,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8cfe207ae03977c612966e473a206ecdbd1796","tid":285111,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n興奮嗎?"},{"pid":"71b929378fb2fd1e156f3e4bae1db1a9faacebc3","tid":285111,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"細細個都咁識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6a00d6f0f9d1e08971ac47900aa2647c2e90d9","tid":285111,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n興奮嗎?</blockquote><br />\n將二人夢一手破壞"},{"pid":"5d5c3d250473c46046153e8b2b42284d740b8267","tid":285111,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n興奮嗎?</blockquote><br />\n氣氛夠激昂嗎?"},{"pid":"cf6279c20c468d4ba96d21c84d7e88e6311d10bd","tid":285111,"uid":28763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:46:39.000Z","msg":"岸本老太婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b8c0fede41bb35c2d0052fa4394c9915ba6c14","tid":285111,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n興奮嗎?</blockquote><br />\n將二人夢一手破壞</blockquote><br />\n悲慘世界"},{"pid":"e9f5b95bbd6b742fadaf3578473d672d33ee46b3","tid":285111,"uid":39064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"crossover<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30620e3942ceee8516d0b964810bda949453595a","tid":285111,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"7c7d8dfa2d9b20989889a2541672c8c90e7cac9b","tid":285111,"uid":4269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"29c48d92d957781d1db1f982a38b962a88b05351","tid":285111,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Old news</blockquote><br />\n唔係好old姐"}]}